# Graphic Charter

Visual identity for the ERP app. This rule is the source of truth for styling.

## Enforcement

- Brand colors and typography must come from `@theme` tokens in `src/index.css`.
- Use semantic Tailwind classes (`bg-background`, `bg-surface`, `text-foreground`, `text-muted`, `bg-primary`, `border-border`) ‚Äî not raw hex or rgb in components.
- Forbidden for brand elements: hardcoded `#‚Ä¶`, `rgb(‚Ä¶)`, or arbitrary Tailwind colors (`bg-[#1a2b3c]`).
- Exception: dynamic institution colors from the API may use inline `style`.
- Reuse the same button, input, card, and badge patterns across pages.
- Mobile-first layouts with Tailwind responsive prefixes.

## Typography

- Font: **Inter** (`--font-sans`)
- Titles: `font-semibold`
- Body: `font-normal`
- Labels: `text-sm uppercase tracking-wide`

## Tailwind Theme Tokens

Map all charter values into `src/index.css` via Tailwind v4 `@theme`. Dark theme is the default; light theme overrides shared tokens.

```css
@import "tailwindcss";

@theme {
  --font-sans: "Inter", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;

  /* Accent ‚Äî shared across themes */
  --color-primary: #117964;
  --color-primary-hover: #1abc9c;
  --color-on-primary: #ffffff;

  /* Semantic ‚Äî dark (default) */
  --color-background: #020f1f;
  --color-surface: #0f2b44;
  --color-surface-hover: #163754;
  --color-border: #274661;
  --color-foreground: #e6edf3;
  --color-muted: #a8bccc;
  --color-disabled: #60758c;

  /* Status ‚Äî shared */
  --color-success: #22c55e;
  --color-warning: #f59e0b;
  --color-danger: #ef4444;

  /* Charts ‚Äî dark */
  --color-chart-1: #1abc9c;
  --color-chart-2: #117964;
  --color-chart-3: #5dade2;
}

/* Light theme overrides */
.light,
[data-theme="light"] {
  @theme {
    --color-background: #f5f8fb;
    --color-surface: #ffffff;
    --color-surface-hover: #eef3f7;
    --color-border: #d8e2ec;
    --color-foreground: #1e293b;
    --color-muted: #64748b;
    --color-disabled: #94a3b8;
    --color-chart-3: #60a5fa;
  }
}
```

| Token | Dark | Light | Tailwind usage |
|-------|------|-------|----------------|
| Background | `#020F1F` Deep Navy | `#F5F8FB` Light Gray | `bg-background` |
| Surface / Cards | `#0F2B44` Navy Surface | `#FFFFFF` White | `bg-surface` |
| Surface hover | `#163754` Elevated | `#EEF3F7` Soft Gray | `bg-surface-hover` |
| Accent | `#117964` Emerald | `#117964` Emerald | `bg-primary`, `text-primary` |
| Accent hover | `#1ABC9C` Emerald Light | `#1ABC9C` Emerald Light | `hover:bg-primary-hover` |
| On primary | `#FFFFFF` White | `#FFFFFF` White | `text-on-primary` |
| Border | `#274661` Soft Border | `#D8E2EC` Light Border | `border-border` |
| Text | `#E6EDF3` Off White | `#1E293B` Dark Slate | `text-foreground` |
| Text muted | `#A8BCCC` Muted Blue | `#64748B` Slate Gray | `text-muted` |
| Disabled | `#60758C` | `#94A3B8` | `text-disabled` |
| Success | `#22C55E` | `#22C55E` | `text-success`, `bg-success` |
| Warning | `#F59E0B` | `#F59E0B` | `text-warning`, `bg-warning` |
| Danger | `#EF4444` | `#EF4444` | `text-danger`, `bg-danger` |

Chart series: `chart-1` `#1ABC9C`, `chart-2` `#117964`, `chart-3` `#5DADE2` (dark) / `#60A5FA` (light).

## Logo

- Icon: calendar (planning / coaching / suivi) ‚Äî `text-primary-hover` (`#1ABC9C`)
- Text primary: `text-foreground` (dark: `#E6EDF3`, light: `#1E293B`)
- Text secondary: `text-muted` (dark: `#A8BCCC`, light: `#64748B`)

## UI Rules

- Dark UI by default ‚Äî never pure black (`#000000`)
- Single accent color (emerald family)
- Soft contrasts, simple professional design
- Rounded corners: `rounded-xl`
- Light shadows only ‚Äî no heavy drop shadows

